items.name: 【再世】next life-计春华
items.description:
这是群星再世第二十二期，以后会不定期出去世的群星Lora，以纪念他们。

计春华，中国影视圈最出名的反派演员，从1988年的《黄河大侠》开始，因凶恶的外表，矫健的身手，被导演挑中饰演电影中的反派“秃鹰”，自此以后的三十多年时间，其参与几百部影视剧中，仅有两次饰演正面人物，还反响平平。

人们更多还是记住了他反派的那一面，甚至成为很多人的童年阴影，计春华在一个访谈节目中还说过，自己因为外表凶狠，有两次被警察带走~~ 而他是光头，没有眉毛，是因为童年时期有一次喝中药，使用的是铝锅熬制中药，那次导致了他中毒，从此以后，他就再也没有了头发和眉毛。

2018年因肺癌晚期去世，享年57岁。

This model is based on anything4.5 trained from the picture of damaobanlangen, and it is recommended to use weights between 0.6 to 0.8.

There have been many controversies about the training and use of art style models, but they are also a difficult part to avoid in the process of AI painting progress.

Therefore, it is recommended to use such art style models as a kind of existence similar to potions, by matching Loras of different art styles with different weights to form images with different styles (although this may lead to bad results, it is worth trying).Alternatively, it can be used to match your favorite character models. Anyway, I hope not to compare it with the artist's own work and make rude remarks, which will harm the community's environment.

At the same time, there are still many problems to be discovered in this model. In short, hope you have a good time.

Brooklyn Danielle Decker (born April 12, 1987) is an American model and actress, perhaps best known for her appearances in the Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue, including the cover of the 2010 issue. In addition to working for Victoria's Secret for the 2010 "Swim" collection, she has ventured into television with guest appearances on Chuck, Ugly Betty, The League, and Royal Pains. She made her feature film debut in Just Go with It (2011), and later starred in Battleship (2012) and What to Expect When You're Expecting (2012). items.name: FireMorph
items.description:
I hope you like hot coffee.

I trained it with just shapes, switched back to LyCoris and played around with the training settings to generate this version of the model.

Thx to rfktr for his helpful input on my water model. I applied what I learned in this model, too.

Works without triggerword, mostly.

When using just the Lora, the fire comes out quite pale. It really makes everything look like fire though, even faces. To counter it, use a weight of around .45-.75 and add "fire" or "vivid fire" to your prompt and you'll get burning rabbits. Have fun setting things on fire.

If you like what I'm creating feel free to buy me a coffee. ;)

I'd like to see your creations, too. Leave a review of your colorful images.

items.name: Phantom Corsair (1938)
items.description:
The Phantom Corsair, also known as the "Flying Wombat," is an iconic concept car that was designed in the 1930s. It was the brainchild of Rust Heinz, the heir to the H. J. Heinz Company fortune, and Maurice Schwartz, an experienced automobile designer.

The Phantom Corsair was intended to be a futuristic luxury automobile with a sleek and aerodynamic design. It featured a low-slung body made of hand-formed aluminum, which gave it a distinctive and streamlined appearance. The car had unique design elements such as hidden wheels, recessed door handles, and an absence of running boards.

Inside, the Phantom Corsair had a luxurious and spacious cabin that could accommodate up to six passengers. It boasted innovative features for its time, including a push-button transmission, power windows, and a built-in radio system. The car was also equipped with advanced engineering, such as a Cord 812 drivetrain, which provided it with impressive performance capabilities.

Despite its innovative design and advanced features, the Phantom Corsair never went into mass production. Only one prototype was ever built, which still exists today and is considered a rare and valuable collector's item. The car made appearances in various films and has gained a cult following over the years due to its unique and futuristic aesthetic.

The Phantom Corsair stands as a testament to the visionary design of the 1930s and continues to be admired as an iconic and influential concept car.

items.name: Confused girls at computers [CONCEPT]
items.description:
Have you ever thought "Man I really need a LoRA to make confused girls sitting at computers"? No? Just me then?

I made this as an experiment to see if it was possible to make a good concept LoRA on just one image and the answer is "no". So I retrained with a second image made by the LoRA itself and the answer became - eh, kinda, fun to play with for a bit so I figured I'd share it.

The art style is very strict but it seems to work OK with character LoRAs. Slightly more reliable using DPM++ 2M Karras, at least on AOM2. Recommended LoRA strength 0.8 to 1.0. Note that the dataset had square images so using other aspect ratios might break things or add more panes.


If anyone wants to use this LoRA to make more images to train on for a better version feel free, no rights reserved whatsoever.


Original image created by the artist naavs.

items.description:
A request of @alextravis8888729.

Débora Gomes is a social media personality from Portugal, with more than 1M followers on Tiktok.

130-step TI trained on a dataset of 15 images with these settings.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Building a good prompt with my TIs

You're obviously free to experiment, but bear in mind that my TIs are trained with a more or less fixed phrasing, that normally starts with:

"photo of EMBEDDING_NAME, a woman"

So I recommend always starting your prompt like that and then building the rest of the prompt from there. For instance, "photo of beautiful (d3borag0mes:0.99), a woman as a movie star, sweater off-shoulders, trousers, at a movie premiere gala, dark moody ambience (masterpiece:1.2) (photorealistic:1.2) (bokeh) (best quality) (detailed skin:1.2) (intricate details) (nighttime) (8k) (HDR) (cinematic lighting) (sharp focus), (looking at the camera:1.1), (closeup portrait:1.1)"

items.name: Inflatable Dolls
items.description:
Turns girls into inflatable dolls with varying boobas, colors, and shinyness. I had to cook this one a lot to get transparent breasts working, so you may need to turn the weight down and parameters up if you want to preserve your model's look. Consequently, it also tends to preserve faces since half the data set had that look. I'll be working on cleaning up the trigger words and features in the future, as well as trying to get it to work with drawing styles.

Works well with semi-realistic or realistic models at a weight of 0.5-1 with "inflatable" in the prompt. Add in colors or glossy skin to get it going. You can kind of trick it into using unsupported colors (up to the neck) by strongly prompting (wearing ______ latex). I also find it fun to mix with the microwaist lora, or use it to make real-ish anime girls. lastly, it also seems to only apply to girls, so you can put men in the scene relatively unaffected 😉

Supported prompts:

glossy skin, shiny skin, pink skin, transparent breasts, orange skin, dark skin, gray skin, big breasts, huge breasts, huge ass

Kind of working prompts (at heavy weights):

transparent skin, light pink skin, inflation valves

Non-working for me, but feel free to try:
light red skin, normal head, inflatable head, popping, inflation, pump, balloon nipples

items.name: John Martin Style
items.description:
John Martin was an English painter and printmaker known for his dramatic and monumental landscapes.

His style can be described as Romantic, characterized by vast, apocalyptic scenes and a sense of awe-inspiring grandeur.

Martin's paintings often depicted cataclysmic events such as floods, storms, and volcanic eruptions, evoking a sense of both awe and terror.

He had a unique ability to capture the sublime power of nature, with swirling clouds, towering cliffs, and cascading waterfalls dominating his compositions.

Martin's use of light and shadow added to the dramatic effect of his works, heightening the emotional impact on the viewer.

His art found great popularity during the 19th century, appealing to the public's fascination with the sublime and the exploration of the unknown.

Today, John Martin's artworks continue to captivate audiences with their epic scale and evocative portrayal of nature's elemental forces.

说实话，我一直对培训资料不感兴趣，每次都去问实际操作培训的问题，在这里非常感谢即将到来的魔老大不辞辛劳的讲解和教学方法。问了两个多月了，我也没有什么好意即将到来了，决定训练一下lora。

附上来魔老大地址：

https://civitai.com/user/comingdemon/models

我还要感谢另一个大佬DukeG，帮我解决了很多技术问题。

感谢AI，我学到了很多东西，认识了很多新朋友，感谢他们的无私帮助。

items.name: Karisma Kapoor
items.description:
Karisma Kapoor is a Bollywood heartthrob from the 90s and early 2000s. Coming from a long line of actors, she was the only actress at the time that could pull of traditional Indian clothing and short skirts with equal aplomb.

Lycos are quirky. This one's quirk is that it needs the 'restore faces' to be turned off. Also used very few negative prompts (see sample images) - otherwise effect of the Lyco quickly reduces.

It is also tending to produce images that look more anime like, but the end results look good, so am uploading. May follow up with a version that looks more photorealistic.

Suggested settings:

  1. Sampler: Euler a, DDIM for first pass, then img2img for upscaling with DPM++ 2M SDE Karras

  2. Steps: 20-30

  3. CFG scale: 6-7.5

  4. Strength: 1-1.25

items.name: colored blindfold
items.description:
我的英文不好，以下来自google翻译

My English is not good, the following is from Google Translate

前言 foreword：

这个lora来自于一个有趣的试验，当我想要设计一些遮着眼睛的角色时，在civitai网站上并没有发现合适的lora，而sd的prompt似乎也是时好时坏，于是我训练了这个lora。

This lora comes from an interesting experiment. When I needed to design some characters wearing blindfolds, I didn't find a suitable lora on the civitai website, and the prompt of sd seemed to be up and down, so I trained this lora.

特点 features：

这个lora可以给任意角色戴上眼罩，并指定颜色，它对角色的干扰很小。我在一些著名的checkpoint上做了验证，并使用了它们图例中的prompt，在没有使用额外的lora和脚本的情况下，它在诸多checkpoint上的表现都很好，每张图都是一次成型，这远超我的预期，希望对你也是一样。

This lora can put blindfolds on any character and specify the color, and it has little interference with the character. I did verification on some famous checkpoints and used the prompts in their legends. Without using additional lora and scripts, it performed very well on many checkpoints, and each graph was formed at one time. , which far exceeded my expectations, and I hope it will be the same for you.

用法 Instructions：

加载lora，并在正向提示词的最前面加上引导词***-blindfold

引导词的权重建议在1~1.3之间

Load lora, and add the guide word ***-blindfold at the front of the positive prompt word

The weight of the guide words is recommended to be between 1 and 1.3

例如 example：

(red-blindfold:1.2), your prompts, <YKHB-000000:0.3>

引导词有各种颜色

blindfold color：

black-blindfold,white-blindfold,red-blindfold,yellow-blindfold,green-blindfold,

采样方法

Sampler：DPM adaptive

CFG：6

Clip skip：2

lora的权重

Lora weight：0.3~0.6

由于该lora使用很低的权重就可以发挥很好的效果，所以你可以把它跟其他lora混合使用，并且不用担心画面遭到破坏。

Since this lora works well with very low weights, you can mix it with other loras without worrying about the picture being destroyed.

其他 other：

使用了92张各种分辨率的图片，在1.5的checkpoint上进行训练，并在10个著名的checkpoint上进行验证，几乎包含了排行榜上所有的写实风格和2.5D风格，checkpoint名单如下：

Using 92 pictures of various resolutions, trained on 1.5 checkpoints, and verified on 10 famous checkpoints, almost including all the realistic styles and 2.5D styles on the leaderboard, the list of checkpoints is as follows:

deliberate

items.name: Cyber Background
items.description:
Introducing Cyber Background Model: An AI Model for Generating Cyberpunk backgrounds.

Cyber Background Model is specifically designed to generate captivating and immersive backgrounds inspired by the cyberpunk genre and neon-lit environments. Trained on a dataset comprising images of cyberpunk cityscapes and neon places, the model has undergone 20 epochs and 1760 steps to master the intricacies and visual characteristics of these futuristic and vibrant settings.

The dataset used to train Cyber Background Model was carefully curated to include a wide range of cyberpunk and neon-inspired images. These images showcase the iconic elements of cyberpunk aesthetics, such as towering futuristic skyscrapers, neon-lit streets, holographic billboards, and bustling cityscapes. By training on this dataset, the model has gained a deep understanding of the visual elements that define cyberpunk and neon environments.

The model used more than 500 high-quality original pictures for training. I am quite satisfied with the overall effect of the model. The body, clothing, movements, etc. are well restored. Because there is no targeted training on the wand, the wand is relatively broken.

The color style can be enhanced with the following Trigger Words: 1990s (style)，retro artstyle

Character style can be emphasized using the following keywords: kinomoto sakura, daidouji tomoyo

The LORA model of other works of CLAMP will continue to be released in the future.

I'd recommend using a weight value 0.6~1.0,

animevae.pt is good for this model,

For my tests I have used scmix_NSM.ckpt

--- --- --- --- --- --- --- ---

该模型使用了超过500张高质量的原始图片进行训练，该模型整体效果我比较满意，身体、服装、动作等都还原的不错，因为并没有针对性对魔杖进行训练，所以魔杖比较崩。

可以使用以下关键词增强色彩风格：1990s (style)，retro artstyle

可以使用以下关键词强调角色风格：kinomoto sakura, daidouji tomoyo

后续将继续发布CLAMP的其他作品LORA模型。

推荐权重：0.6~1.0
